  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf 100 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The 100-day struggle for a political solution for the Tamil people begins in Mannar on the first day",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The coordinator of the North East Coordination Committee, Kandumani Lavakusarasa said that the 100-day vigil protest will begin in Mannar on the first day of the next day and will continue in 8 districts in the North East.",
        "The coordinator of the North East Coordination Committee Kandumani Lavakusarasa issued a media statement today Saturday (30).",
        "The 100-day campaign of 'People's voice for a political solution with dignified rights' was organized as usual under the auspices of the North East Coordination Committee in 08 districts of the North East on a rotating basis by the people living in the North East, village grassroots organizations, farmers', fishermen's associations, women's organizations and students' organizations, civil organizations. to be carried out.",
        "Day 1 of the said 100-day campaign will be launched on the first day of the People's Voice in Mannar district.",
        "Following this, arrangements have been made for this protest to be held in other districts in a continuous cycle.",
        "So all Tamil people in this democratic struggle; It is pointed out in the statement that we will participate and work out a political solution for us."
      ],
